Package: exportr
Title: What the Package Does (One Line, Title Case)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Koffi Dodji", "Noumonvi", email = "bravemaster102@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3305-174X"))
Description: Provides enhanced versions of common data export functions 
    (fwrite, write.csv, saveRDS) that automatically track data provenance.
    Records information about the source script, execution environment, 
    and data characteristics. Offers flexible metadata storage options 
    including CSV comments, central logs, object attributes, or separate files.
